# BZ Reaction Differential Equation Simulation (C++)

This repository now contains:

- `docs/bz_model_and_simulation.md`: mathematical modeling guide from ODE to reaction–diffusion PDE.
- `src/main.cpp`: a standalone C++ Oregonator-style 2D reaction–diffusion simulator that outputs PPM frames.

## Build

```bash
g++ -std=c++17 -O2 -o bz_sim src/main.cpp
```

## Run

```bash
./bz_sim
```

Frames are written to `output/frame_XXXXX.ppm`.

Optional video assembly:

```bash
ffmpeg -framerate 25 -i output/frame_%05d.ppm -pix_fmt yuv420p bz.mp4
```
